{{Expand |time=2010-06-21T19:27:04+00:00 }}
{{ Otheruses|subject=經過城市規劃興建的小型城市|other=經過規劃大城市邊緣的大型城市|新市鎮}}

'''衛星城市'''，是[[城市規劃|城市規劃]]的一個概念，意指[[大城市|大城市]]邊緣的小型[[城市|城市]]，為在大都市工作者主要的居住地<ref>{{Cite book| url=https://books.google.com/books?id=yWA5DQAAQBAJ&pg=PT815| title=Encyclopedia of American Urban History| isbn=9780761928843| last1=Goldfield| first1=David| year=2007| access-date=2021-02-01| archive-date=2021-05-09| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210509041745/https://books.google.com/books?id=yWA5DQAAQBAJ&pg=PT815| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url = https://books.google.com/books?id=eq1nCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA25|title = The New Urban Area Development: A Case Study in China|isbn = 9783662449585|last1 = Shao|first1 = Zisheng|date = 19 August 2015|access-date = 2021-02-01|archive-date = 2021-05-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210509041725/https://books.google.com/books?id=eq1nCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA25|dead-url = no}}</ref>。因为如[[卫星|卫星]]般与[[大城市|大城市]]相近，故称之。

